p; &nbsp; INX<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CPX #$10<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; BNE LBL.NMI.LoadPalettes.Sprites.Loop<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />LBL.NMI.LoadPalette.Background:<br />&nbsp; LDA FLAG.NMI.Update.Background.Palette<br />&nbsp; BEQ LBL.NMI.UpdateSprites<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; LDA $2002<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; LDA #$3F<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; STA $2006<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; LDA #$00<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; STA $2006&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; LDX #$00<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; LBL.NMI.LoadPalettes.Background.Loop:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; LDA BUF.Palette.Background, X<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; STA $2007<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; INX<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CPX #$10<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; BNE LBL.NMI.LoadPalettes.Background.Loop<br />&nbsp; <br /><br /><br />LBL.NMI.UpdateSprites:<br />&nbsp; LDA FLAG.NMI.Update.Sprites<br />&nbsp; BEQ LBL.NMI.Exit<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; LDA #$00<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; STA $2003<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; LDA #&gt;BUF.Sprites<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; STA $4014<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;LDA FALSE<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; STA FLAG.NMI.Update.Sprites&nbsp; &nbsp;<br /><br />LBL.NMI.Exit:<br />&nbsp; LDA #%10001000<br />&nbsp; STA $2000<br />&nbsp; LDA #$00<br />&nbsp; STA $2005<br />&nbsp; STA $2005<br />&nbsp; INC VAR.Frame<br />&nbsp; PLA<br />&nbsp; TAY<br />&nbsp; PLA<br />&nbsp; TAX<br />&nbsp; PLA<br />&nbsp; RTI<br /></div></div>

