						<div class="postbody">Ah, I misunderstood what was going on - that's what I get for not fully reading the entire thread.<br /><br />One solution to this problem is to just ensure that an NMI will never occur during VRAM writes - either disable NMI during any VRAM writes (which is probably a good idea anyways), or schedule them to occur during your NMI routine.</div>

					
